Title: An Act Changing the Name of the Labakid Elementary School in Barangay Labakid, Municipality of Sindangan, Province of Zamboanga Del Norte, to Apolonio Molina Elementary School
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 217
An Act Changing the Name of the Labakid Elementary School in Barangay Labakid, Municipality of Sindangan, Province of Zamboanga Del Norte, to Apolonio Molina Elementary School
Section 1. The name of the Labakid Elementary School in Barangay Labakid, Municipality of Sindangan, Province of Zamboanga del Norte, is hereby changed to Apolonio Molina Elementary School.1Ã¢wphi1
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Approved: March 25, 1982
